@NODE "AllocText" "AllocText"
@TOC "MAIN"

Function         : AllocText

Prototype        : long AllocText( struct @{"SubboardType4" LINK "cnetinclude:subs.h/main" 439} *s, long length );

Purpose          : Allocate a block of subboard data text.

Arguments        : s      - the subboard in which the desired text is to be
                            allocated
                   length - the desired length of text to allocate

Returns          : location (seek value) pertaining to the start of the block
                   of text allocated.

