See also         : @{"FreeText" LINK "FreeText"}
@ENDNODE

@NODE "AlterDate" "AlterDate"
@TOC "MAIN"

Function         : AlterDate

Prototype        : void AlterDate( struct @{"IsDate" LINK "cnetinclude:dates.h/main" 4} *date, long i );

Purpose          : Alter an IsDate structure by a given number of days.

Arguments        : date - the IsDate structure to alter.
                   i    - the number of days by which to alter the date.

Returns          : none

Known bugs       : none

See Also         : 
