@NODE "AppendToFile" "AppendToFile"
@TOC "MAIN"

Function         : AppendToFile

Prototype        : BOOL AppendToFile( char *filename, char *text, BOOL AddCR);

Purpose          : add text to a file with or without appending newline (0x0A)

Arguments        : filename - the full path/filename of the destination file.
                   text     - the text to be added to the destination file.
                   AddCR    - FALSE to suppress newline.
                              TRUE to add newline.

Returns          : TRUE on success; FALSE if error.
                   
Known bugs       : none

See also         : 
