                             or a pointer to the string "%s %2d-%s-%d %2d:%02d%c"
                   tz      - integer representing the output time zone with
                             reference to the BBS time zone.
                   form    - 0 = AM/PM format
                             1 = 24 hour format

Returns          : none

Known bugs       : none

See also         : 
