Purpose          : Initialize a cache entry for the user belonging to the
                   specified account.

Notes            : Do NOT call this function on a previously initialized user.
                   Check for this case by using @{"UCacheLookup()" LINK "UCacheLookup"} first.
                   
                   In general, the user cache functions should not be required
                   as @{"LockAccount()" LINK "LockAccount"} and @{"UnLockAccount()" LINK "UnLockAccount"} support user cacheing
                   internally.

Arguments        : account - the account number of the user to cache.

Returns          : pointer to the initialized user cache entry
                   
Known bugs       : none

See also         : 
@ENDNODE

